    %h3 Deploying to Heroku

    %ol
      %li Make sure you are already in your project directory and that all your changes have been committed – Heroku deploys your <em>last commit</em>.
      %li Type <code>heroku create</code> to setup a new Heroku site (just have to do this once)
      %li Type <code>git push heroku master</code> any time you want to deploy

    %p To check your Heroku logs: <code>heroku logs --tail</code> (press Ctrl+C when you're done)

