    %h3 Homework: your project

    %p By next Tuesday evening, please submit the beginnings of a plan for your final project. Some things that I want to discuss with you before you do any coding are:

    %ul
      %li Drawings of each of the screens of your web app – these can be really rough – we will use these to spec the functionality you’ll be building
      %li Your database structure – what tables you’ll have, what fields, and how they will be related

    %p You don’t have to submit everything, but you do have to submit something. If in doubt, ask. I can guarantee responses if you email my by Sunday night. Any later and I may not have time.
